displayName: West End City - Self Defence Force HQ

parameters: \n<Soldier>We don't allow yer kind in our base!\.\. Go to th' counter if ye want to take a job.
"1.\.\. Citizen of End City are precious workforce,\. and aren't allowed to risk their lives by embarking in dangerous quests."
"2.\.\. Only registered members of the SDC are allowed to take any request beyond the lowest level."
"3.\.\. Travellers and foreigners,\. who aren't working to ensure End City's prosperity,\. are allowed to take any quest compliant to the SDC's mission."
